else if (Q.agriculture_minister_party === 'WP') Q.agriculture_minister = 'Bredt';
else if (Q.agriculture_minister_party === 'CNBL') Q.agriculture_minister = 'Hamkens';
else if (Q.agriculture_minister_party === 'DNVP') Q.agriculture_minister = 'Schiele';
else Q.agriculture_minister = 'Unbesetzt';

// Transport Ministry
if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'KPD') Q.agriculture_minister = 'Hoernle';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'SAPD') Q.transport_minister = 'Baade';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'SPD') Q.transport_minister = 'Baade';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'SRPD') Q.transport_minister = 'Baade';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'DDP') Q.transport_minister = 'Dietrich';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'Z') Q.transport_minister = 'Guerard';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'BVP') Q.transport_minister = 'Wutzlhofer';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'DVP') Q.transport_minister = 'Schiele';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'WP') Q.transport_minister = 'Bredt';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'CNBL') Q.transport_minister = 'Hamkens';
else if (Q.transport_minister_party === 'DNVP') Q.transport_minister = 'Schiele';
else Q.transport_minister = 'Unbesetzt';

// Reichswehr always independent
Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Groener';
Q.reichswehr_minister_party = 'I';

// Store allocation for display
Q.ministry_allocation = allocation;
Q.ministry_leverage = leverage;

// HINDENBURG'S STATUS UPDATE
Q.hindenburg_patience += 10



!}

= Cabinet Formation Complete

**The [+ coalition_name +] has formed its cabinet:**

**Ministries by Party:**

[+ ministry_display_list +]

**Cabinet Appointments:**
- **Foreign Ministry:** [+ foreign_minister_party +] - [+ foreign_minister +]
- **Interior Ministry:** [+ interior_minister_party +] - [+ interior_minister +]
- **Justice Ministry:** [+ justice_minister_party +] - [+ justice_minister +]
- **Labor Ministry:** [+ labor_minister_party +] - [+ labor_minister +]
- **Economic Affairs:** [+ economic_minister_party +] - [+ economic_minister +]
- **Finance Ministry:** [+ finance_minister_party +] - [+ finance_minister +]
- **Agriculture Ministry:** [+ agriculture_minister_party +] - [+ agriculture_minister +]
- **Transport Ministry:** [+ transport_minister_party +] [+ transport_minister +]
- **Reichswehr Ministry:** Independent - [+ reichswehr_minister +]

[? if foreign_minister = 'Unbesetzt' or interior_minister = 'Unbesetzt' or justice_minister = 'Unbesetzt' : **Warning:** Some ministries remain unfilled and will operate under civil service administration. ?]

[? if kpd_in_government : The KPD has entered government for the first time. The revolutionary left now holds state power. ?]

[? if in_left_front : KPD ministers will push for radical socialist policies. Internal dissent is likely. ?]

[? if in_popular_front : This unprecedented coalition will face severe pressure from both the far-left and far-right. ?]

- @hitler_crushed: Reactionaries are ousted.
- @root: Continue on...
- @ministry_renegotiation

@hitler_crushed
subtitle: Time of reaction has ended.
view-if: ((spd_r + ddp_r + z_r + (dvp_r / dvp_right_shift) + srpd_r + sapd_r) > nsdap_r) and civil_war_end_modifier_national = 1
on-arrival: civil_war_end_modifier_national = 0

Period of the fear against [+ president +] has ended and we may finally rest freely as the democracy is saved once more by us and our allies...

- @root: Democracy marches on...

@coalition_failure
on-arrival: {!
// ============================================
// COALITION FORMATION FAILED
// ============================================

Q.formation_round++;
Q.no_majority_elections = Q.no_majority_elections || 0;

// Store the failed party name BEFORE moving to next
Q.failed_formateur = Q.formateur;

// Pre-calculate current formateur votes for display
Q.formateur_votes = Q[Q.formateur.toLowerCase() + '_r'];

// Find next viable formateur
Q.next_formateur_found = 0;

for (var i = Q.formation_round - 1; i < Q.party_votes.length; i++) {
    var candidate = Q.party_votes[i].party;
    
    // Skip impossible formateurs
    if (candidate === 'NSDAP' && Q.nsdap_r < 40) continue;
    if (candidate === 'KPD' && Q.communist_coalition < 3) continue;
    if (Q.formation_attempts.indexOf(candidate) >= 0) continue; // Already tried
    
    Q.formateur = candidate;
    Q.formateur_votes = Q[Q.formateur.toLowerCase() + '_r']; // Update votes for new formateur
    Q.next_formateur_found = 1;
    break;
}

Q.all_attempts_failed = !Q.next_formateur_found || Q.formation_round > Q.party_votes.length;

// If all attempts failed, check if we should call elections or presidential cabinet
if (Q.all_attempts_failed) {
    Q.no_majority_elections++; // Increment counter
}
!}
go-to: call_new_elections if all_attempts_failed and no_majority_elections < 2; presidential_crisis if all_attempts_failed and no_majority_elections >= 2; next_formateur_attempt if not all_attempts_failed

@next_formateur_attempt

= Formation Attempt Failed

**[+ failed_formateur +] has failed to form a viable coalition.**

The mandate now passes to **[+ formateur +]** ([+ formateur_votes +]%).

[? if formation_round >= 3 : The political crisis deepens as multiple parties have failed to form a government. ?]

- @begin_negotiations: [+ formateur +] begins coalition negotiations

@call_new_elections
on-arrival: {!
Q.new_elections_imminent = 1;
Q.next_election_month = Q.month + 2;
Q.next_election_year = Q.year;
if (Q.next_election_month > 12) {
    Q.next_election_month -= 12;
    Q.next_election_year += 1;
}
Q.next_election_time = Q.time + 2;

// Temporary caretaker government
Q.in_minority_government = 1;
Q.caretaker_government = 1;

// Political consequences
Q.pro_republic -= 3;
Q.workers_spd -= 2;
Q.new_middle_spd -= 1;
Q.political_crisis_level += 1;
!}

= Coalition Formation Impossible - New Elections

**No viable coalition could be formed.**

All major parties have attempted and failed to build a majority government. The Reichstag is deadlocked.

[? if no_majority_elections = 1 : This is the first time we've failed to form a government. ?]

President [+ president +] has dissolved the Reichstag and called for new elections to be held in **[+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +]**.

A caretaker government will administer until then, but cannot pass major legislation or implement significant policy changes.

**Political Impact:**
- Public frustration with parliamentary democracy grows
- Extremist parties will use this deadlock in their campaigns
- Coalition negotiations will resume after the election

[? if no_majority_elections = 1 : If the next election also produces no viable coalition, the President may be forced to appoint a minority government under Article 48. ?]

- @accept_elections: Accept the electoral solution

@accept_elections
on-arrival: coalition_dissent += 3; left_dissent += 5

New elections have been scheduled. The campaign will be dominated by questions about governmental stability.

Our party must prepare for what may be a crucial electoral test.










@presidential_crisis
on-arrival: {!
// ============================================
// NO COALITION POSSIBLE - PRESIDENTIAL CRISIS
// After 2+ consecutive failed coalition attempts
// ============================================

Q.presidential_government = 1;
Q.in_minority_government = 1;
Q.spd_in_government = 0;
Q.kpd_in_government = 0;
Q.presidential_cabinet = true;

// All ministries default to independent/civil service
Q.foreign_minister_party = 'I';
Q.interior_minister_party = 'I';
Q.justice_minister_party = 'I';
Q.labor_minister_party = 'I';
Q.economic_minister_party = 'I';
Q.finance_minister_party = 'I';
Q.agriculture_minister_party = 'I';
Q.reichswehr_minister_party = 'I';
Q.transport_minister_party = 'I';

Q.transport_minister_party = 'I';
Q.transport_minister = 'von Guérard';

Q.foreign_minister = 'von Schubert';
Q.interior_minister = 'Zweigert';
Q.justice_minister = 'Joël';
Q.labor_minister = 'Brauns';
Q.economic_minister = 'von Raumer';
Q.finance_minister = 'von Schlieben';
Q.agriculture_minister = 'von Kanitz';
Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Groener';

// President's choice of minority chancellor
// ========================================
// HINDENBURG'S CHANCELLOR SELECTION
// ========================================

if (Q.president === "Hindenburg") {

    // ============================================================
    // HINDENBURG PRESIDENTIAL CABINET SELECTION
    // Reads camarilla system outputs produced in post_event.
    // All scoring is done there — here we just rank and pick.
    // ============================================================

    var cam_scores  = Q.camarilla_chancellor_scores || {};
    var cam_goals   = Q.camarilla_goals || {};
    var cam_str     = Q.camarilla_strength || 0;
    var cam_ceil    = Q.camarilla_ceiling  || 120;

    var install_goal     = cam_goals.install_hitler     || 0;
    var crush_left_goal  = cam_goals.crush_left         || 0;
    var destroy_parl     = cam_goals.destroy_parliament || 0;
    var protect_junkers  = cam_goals.protect_junkers    || 0;

    var hindenburg_weak   = (Q.hindenburg_health   || 100) < 60
                         || (Q.hindenburg_senility || 0)   >= 40;
    var hindenburg_puppet = (Q.hindenburg_senility || 0)   >= 60
                         || cam_str >= 90;

    var severe_crisis      = Q.unemployed >= 18 || Math.abs(Q.inflation) >= 8  || Q.economic_growth < -5;
    var catastrophic_crisis = Q.unemployed >= 25 || Math.abs(Q.inflation) >= 12 || Q.economic_growth < -8;

    // --- Candidate pool ---
    // Each entry: { name, party, type, base_score }
    // base_score built from camarilla outputs + member influence + economic state
    var candidates = [];

    // === PARLIAMENTARY CENTRISTS ===
    // Viable while Reichstag trust is reasonable
    var rt = Q.hindenburg_trust_reichstag || 50;
    if (rt >= 30 && !hindenburg_puppet) {

        if (Q.z_r >= 10) {
            if (Q.z_party_leader === "Brüning" || Q.z_leader === "Brüning") {
                candidates.push({
                    name: "Brüning", party: "Z", type: "parliamentary",
                    base_score: (cam_scores["Brüning"] || 0)
                              + (Q.hindenburg_trust_z || 60) * 0.5
                              + (Q.meissner_influence || 55) * 0.15
                              + (severe_crisis ? 20 : 0)
                });
            }
            if (Q.z_party_leader === "Marx" || Q.z_leader === "Marx") {
                candidates.push({
                    name: "Marx", party: "Z", type: "parliamentary",
                    base_score: (cam_scores["Marx"] || 0)
                              + (Q.hindenburg_trust_z || 60) * 0.4
                              + (Q.year <= 1928 ? 15 : -5)
                });
            }
            if (Q.z_party_leader === "Wirth" || Math.random() < 0.3) {
                candidates.push({
                    name: "Wirth", party: "Z", type: "parliamentary",
                    base_score: (cam_scores["Wirth"] || -10)
                              + (Q.hindenburg_trust_z || 60) * 0.3
                              + (Q.spd_in_government ? 8 : -8)
                });
            }
        }

        if (Q.dvp_r >= 6) {
            if (!Q.stresemann_dead) {
                candidates.push({
                    name: "Stresemann", party: "DVP", type: "parliamentary",
                    base_score: (cam_scores["Stresemann"] || 0) + 20
                              + (Q.dvp_r * 0.8)
                });
            }
            candidates.push({
                name: "Curtius", party: "DVP", type: "parliamentary",
                base_score: (cam_scores["Curtius"] || 0)
                          + (Q.dvp_r * 0.6)
                          + (Q.economic_minister === "Curtius" ? 8 : 0)
            });
        }

        if (Q.dnvp_r >= 8
            && Q.dnvp_leader !== "Hugenberg"
            && Q.dnvp_party_leader !== "Hugenberg") {
            candidates.push({
                name: "Westarp", party: "DNVP", type: "parliamentary",
                base_score: (cam_scores["Westarp"] || 0)
                          + (Q.hindenburg_trust_dnvp || 70) * 0.5
                          + protect_junkers * 0.15
            });
        }
    }

    // === PRESIDENTIAL TECHNOCRATS ===
    // Grow in importance as camarilla / crisis rises
    var tech_weight = (cam_str / cam_ceil) + (severe_crisis ? 0.3 : 0);

    if (Q.z_r >= 12 && !hindenburg_puppet) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Brüning", party: "Z", type: "presidential_technocrat",
            base_score: (cam_scores["Brüning"] || 0)
                      + (Q.meissner_influence || 55) * 0.6
                      + tech_weight * 25
        });
    }

    if ((Q.goerdeler_prominence || 0) >= 2) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Goerdeler", party: "I", type: "presidential_technocrat",
            base_score: (cam_scores["Goerdeler"] || 0)
                      + (Q.goerdeler_prominence || 0) * 8
                      + (Q.meissner_influence || 55) * 0.4
                      + (cam_str < 60 ? 15 : -10)
        });
    }

    if (Math.random() < 0.35) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Luther", party: "I", type: "presidential_technocrat",
            base_score: 35 + (Q.meissner_influence || 55) * 0.3
                      + (Q.inflation < 0 ? 10 : 0)
        });
    }

    // === ARISTOCRATIC CAMARILLA ===
    // Papen and peers — only viable with strong camarilla or weak Hindenburg
    if (cam_str >= 50 || hindenburg_weak) {

        if ((Q.papen_in_camarilla || Q.year >= 1932)
            && (Q.papen_influence || 0) >= 40) {
            candidates.push({
                name: "Papen", party: "I", type: "aristocrat",
                base_score: (cam_scores["Papen"] || 0)
                          + (Q.papen_influence  || 0) * 0.8
                          + (Q.oskar_influence  || 0) * 0.4
                          + destroy_parl * 0.3
            });
        }

        if (cam_str >= 65 && Math.random() < 0.25) {
            candidates.push({
                name: "von Gayl", party: "I", type: "aristocrat",
                base_score: cam_str * 0.5
                          + (Q.oldenburg_influence || 45) * 0.3
            });
        }
    }

    // === MILITARY ===
    var mil_weight = (cam_str / cam_ceil)
                   + (catastrophic_crisis ? 0.4 : 0)
                   + ((Q.hindenburg_trust_military || 60) > 70 ? 0.2 : 0);

    if ((Q.schleicher_influence || 0) >= 50) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Schleicher", party: "I", type: "military",
            base_score: (cam_scores["Schleicher"] || 0)
                      + (Q.schleicher_influence || 0) * 0.9
                      + mil_weight * 20
                      + (Q.reichswehr_minister === "Schleicher" ? 15 : 0)
        });
    }

    if (Q.reichswehr_minister === "Groener" && !Q.groener_dismissed) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Groener", party: "I", type: "military",
            base_score: 50 + (Q.hindenburg_trust_military || 60) * 0.4
                      + ((Q.reichswehr_loyalty || 0.5) >= 0.6 ? 10 : -10)
        });
    }

    if ((Q.reichswehr_loyalty || 0.5) >= 0.5 && Q.nsdap_r >= 20) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Hammerstein", party: "I", type: "military",
            base_score: (cam_scores["Hammerstein"] || 0)
                      + (Q.reichswehr_loyalty || 0.5) * 60
                      + (install_goal >= 50 ? -25 : 15)
        });
    }

    // === NAZI APPOINTMENT ===
    if (Q.nsdap_r >= 25 && !Q.hitler_appointment_prevented) {
        var nazi_score = 0;
        nazi_score += Math.pow(Q.nsdap_r / 40, 1.5) * 30;
        nazi_score += (cam_scores["Hitler"] || 0);
        nazi_score += install_goal * 0.6;
        if (hindenburg_puppet)    nazi_score += 35;
        else if ((Q.hindenburg_senility || 0) >= 40) nazi_score += 20;
        if (catastrophic_crisis)  nazi_score += 30;
        else if (severe_crisis)   nazi_score += 15;
        if (Q.dnvp_party_leader === "Hugenberg"
            && Q.nsdap_r + Q.dnvp_r >= 40) nazi_score += 25;
        if ((Q.papen_influence || 0) >= 70
            && (Q.oskar_influence || 0) >= 70) nazi_score += 20;

        if (nazi_score > 0) {
            candidates.push({
                name: "Hitler", party: "NSDAP", type: "nazi",
                base_score: nazi_score
            });
        }
    }

    // === SCORE + SELECT ===
    for (var i = 0; i < candidates.length; i++) {
        var c = candidates[i];
        // Crisis penalty for low-tolerance types
        if (severe_crisis && c.type === "aristocrat") c.base_score -= 15;
        if (severe_crisis && c.type === "parliamentary" && !hindenburg_weak) c.base_score -= 5;
        // Camarilla veto on parliamentary options when camarilla dominant
        if (cam_str >= cam_ceil * 0.8 && c.type === "parliamentary") c.base_score *= 0.5;
        // Variance
        c.base_score *= (0.85 + Math.random() * 0.30);
    }

    candidates.sort(function(a, b) { return b.base_score - a.base_score; });

    if (candidates.length > 0) {
        var selected = candidates[0];
        Q.chancellor       = selected.name;
        Q.chancellor_party = selected.party;

        if (selected.type === "presidential_technocrat"
            || selected.type === "aristocrat"
            || selected.type === "military") {
            Q.presidential_cabinet       = 1;
            Q.presidential_cabinet_count = (Q.presidential_cabinet_count || 0) + 1;
        }
        if (selected.name === "Papen")     { Q.papen_cabinet = 1; Q.cabinet_of_barons = 1; }
        if (selected.name === "Schleicher") Q.schleicher_cabinet = 1;
        if (selected.name === "Brüning")    Q.bruning_cabinet = 1;
        if (selected.type === "military" && selected.name !== "Schleicher")
            Q.military_emergency_government = 1;
        if (selected.type === "nazi") {
            Q.nazi_takeover_begins  = 1;
            Q.vice_chancellor       = "Papen";
            Q.vice_chancellor_party = "I";
            Q.cabinet_of_barons     = 1;
        }

    } else {
        Q.chancellor       = "Brüning";
        Q.chancellor_party = "Z";
        Q.presidential_cabinet = 1;
    }

    // Catastrophic collapse override
    if (catastrophic_crisis
        && (Q.hindenburg_trust_military || 60) >= 70
        && (Q.hindenburg_trust_reichstag || 50) < 25) {
        Q.chancellor = (Q.reichswehr_loyalty || 0.5) >= 0.5 ? "Hammerstein" : "Schleicher";
        Q.chancellor_party = "I";
        Q.military_emergency_government = 1;
        Q.article_48_permanent = 1;
    }
    
} else if (Q.president === "Braun") {
    // Braun forms SPD presidential cabinet
    Q.chancellor_party = "SPD";
    Q.chancellor = Q.muller_dead ? "Wels" : "Braun";
    Q.spd_in_government = 1;
    Q.in_emergency_government = 1;
    Q.presidential_powers_active = 1;

    Q.foreign_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.interior_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.justice_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.labor_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.economic_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.finance_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.agriculture_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.reichswehr_minister_party = 'SPD';
    Q.transport_minister_party = 'SPD';

    Q.foreign_minister = 'Breitscheid';
    Q.interior_minister = 'Severing';
    Q.justice_minister = 'Radbruch';
    Q.labor_minister = 'Wisell';
    Q.economic_minister = 'Hilferding';
    Q.finance_minister = 'Hilferding';
    Q.agriculture_minister = 'Baade';
    Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Leber';
    Q.transport_minister = 'Oeser';

} else if (Q.president === "Hitler") {
    // Hitler forms NSDAP presidential cabinet
    Q.chancellor_party = "NSDAP";
    Q.chancellor = Q.year >= 1934 ? "Goring" : "Goebbels";
    Q.nsdap_in_government = 1;
    Q.pro_republic -= 10;
    Q.nationalism += 5;
    Q.rb_strength /= 0.9;
    Q.sa_strength *= 1.1;
    Q.presidential_powers_active = 1;
} else if (Q.president === "Westarp") {
    var westarp_candidates = [];

    // Preferred: DNVP, then DVP, then Z
    if (Q.dnvp_r >= 5) {
        westarp_candidates.push({
            name: Q.dnvp_line === 3 ? "Hugenberg" : "Westarp",
            party: "DNVP",
            score: 80 + (Q.dnvp_line === 3 ? 10 : 0)
        });
        if (Q.dnvp_line !== 3) {
            westarp_candidates.push({name: "Treviranus", party: "DNVP", score: 55});
        }
    }
    if (Q.dvp_r >= 5) {
        westarp_candidates.push({
            name: Q.stresemann_dead ? "Curtius" : "Stresemann",
            party: "DVP",
            score: Q.stresemann_dead ? 45 : 60
        });
        westarp_candidates.push({name: "Dingeldey", party: "DVP", score: 35});
    }
    if (Q.z_r >= 8) {
        westarp_candidates.push({
            name: Q.z_party_leader === "Kaas" ? "Kaas" : "Brüning",
            party: "Z",
            score: Q.z_party_leader === "Kaas" ? 40 : 30
        });
    }
    // Presidential technocrat fallback
    westarp_candidates.push({name: "Luther", party: "I", score: 25});
    westarp_candidates.push({name: "Papen",  party: "I", score: 20});

    westarp_candidates.sort(function(a, b) {
        return (b.score * (0.85 + Math.random() * 0.3)) -
               (a.score * (0.85 + Math.random() * 0.3));
    });

    Q.chancellor       = westarp_candidates[0].name;
    Q.chancellor_party = westarp_candidates[0].party;
    Q.in_right_coalition = 1;
    Q.presidential_powers_active = 1;
    Q.presidential_cabinet = (westarp_candidates[0].party === 'I') ? 1 : 0;

    Q.foreign_minister_party  = 'DVP';
    Q.interior_minister_party = 'DNVP';
    Q.justice_minister_party  = 'Z';
    Q.labor_minister_party    = 'I';
    Q.economic_minister_party = 'DVP';
    Q.finance_minister_party  = 'DNVP';
    Q.agriculture_minister_party = 'CNBL';
    Q.reichswehr_minister_party  = 'I';
    Q.transport_minister_party   = 'I';

    Q.foreign_minister    = Q.stresemann_dead ? 'Curtius' : 'Stresemann';
    Q.interior_minister   = Q.dnvp_line === 3 ? 'Hugenberg' : 'Hergt';
    Q.justice_minister    = Q.z_party_leader === 'Kaas' ? 'Kaas' : 'Bredt';
    Q.labor_minister      = 'Brauns';
    Q.economic_minister   = 'Curtius';
    Q.finance_minister    = 'Schiele';
    Q.agriculture_minister = 'Hamkens';
    Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Groener';
    Q.transport_minister  = 'von Guérard';

    Q.pro_republic  -= 12;
    Q.workers_spd   -= 4;
    Q.left_dissent  += 10;
    Q.coup_progress += 1;
    if (Q.dnvp_line === 3) Q.coup_progress += 2;

} else if (Q.president === "Thälmann" || Q.president === "Thalmann") {
    var thal_candidates = [];

    // Back the left — KPD first, then SAPD, then SPD
    if (Q.kpd_r >= 5) {
        thal_candidates.push({
            name: Q.kpd_party_leader === "Conciliators" ? "Neumann" : "Thälmann",
            party: "KPD",
            score: 90
        });
        thal_candidates.push({name: "Pieck", party: "KPD", score: 70});
    }
    if (Q.sapd_formed && Q.sapd_r >= 3) {
        thal_candidates.push({name: "Rosenfeld", party: "SAPD", score: 55});
        thal_candidates.push({name: "Seydewitz",  party: "SAPD", score: 45});
    }
    if (Q.spd_r >= 5) {
        thal_candidates.push({
            name: Q.muller_dead ? "Wels" : "Müller",
            party: "SPD",
            score: 40
        });
        thal_candidates.push({name: "Breitscheid", party: "SPD", score: 30});
    }
    if (Q.srpd_formed && Q.srpd_r >= 3) {
        thal_candidates.push({name: "Horsing", party: "SRPD", score: 35});
    }

    thal_candidates.sort(function(a, b) {
        return (b.score * (0.85 + Math.random() * 0.3)) -
               (a.score * (0.85 + Math.random() * 0.3));
    });

    Q.chancellor       = thal_candidates.length > 0 ? thal_candidates[0].name  : "Thälmann";
    Q.chancellor_party = thal_candidates.length > 0 ? thal_candidates[0].party : "KPD";
    Q.kpd_in_government = (Q.chancellor_party === 'KPD') ? 1 : 0;
    Q.spd_in_government = (Q.chancellor_party === 'SPD' || Q.chancellor_party === 'SRPD') ? 1 : 0;
    Q.presidential_powers_active = 1;

    // Cabinet leans left — KPD fills what it can, SPD gets labor/justice
    Q.foreign_minister_party  = 'KPD';
    Q.interior_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.justice_minister_party  = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'SPD' : 'KPD';
    Q.labor_minister_party    = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'SPD' : 'KPD';
    Q.economic_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.finance_minister_party  = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'SPD' : 'KPD';
    Q.agriculture_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.reichswehr_minister_party  = 'KPD';
    Q.transport_minister_party   = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'SPD' : 'KPD';

    Q.foreign_minister    = 'Pieck';
    Q.interior_minister   = 'Ulbricht';
    Q.justice_minister    = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'Radbruch' : 'Heckert';
    Q.labor_minister      = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'Wissell'  : 'Münzenberg';
    Q.economic_minister   = 'Remmele';
    Q.finance_minister    = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'Hilferding' : 'Neumann';
    Q.agriculture_minister = 'Hoernle';
    Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Leber';
    Q.transport_minister  = Q.spd_r >= 5 ? 'Oeser' : 'Hoernle';

    Q.pro_republic        -= 15;
    Q.coup_progress       += 4;
    Q.capital_strike_progress += 3;
    Q.reichswehr_loyalty  -= 0.2;
    Q.sa_strength         += 250;
    Q.sh_strength         += 150;
    Q.workers_spd         -= 3;
    Q.left_dissent        -= 8;

} else if (Q.president === "Eckener") {
    // Eckener: technocratic, non-partisan, stability-focused
    Q.chancellor_party = "I";
    Q.chancellor = "Eckener";
    Q.presidential_cabinet = 1;
    Q.presidential_powers_active = 1;

    Q.foreign_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.interior_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.justice_minister_party = 'DDP';
    Q.labor_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.economic_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.finance_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.agriculture_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.reichswehr_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.transport_minister_party = 'I';

    Q.foreign_minister = 'von Schubert';
    Q.interior_minister = 'Zweigert';
    Q.justice_minister = 'Koch-Weser';
    Q.labor_minister = 'Brauns';
    Q.economic_minister = 'von Raumer';
    Q.finance_minister = 'Luther';
    Q.agriculture_minister = 'von Kanitz';
    Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Groener';
    Q.transport_minister = 'von Guérard';

    Q.pro_republic += 3;
    Q.coalition_dissent -= 1;

} else if (Q.president === "Thälmann" || Q.president === "Thalmann") {
    // Thälmann: KPD revolutionary government
    Q.chancellor_party = "KPD";
    Q.chancellor = Q.kpd_party_leader === "Conciliators" ? "Neumann" : "Thälmann";
    Q.kpd_in_government = 1;
    Q.presidential_powers_active = 1;

    Q.foreign_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.interior_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.justice_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.labor_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.economic_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.finance_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.agriculture_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.reichswehr_minister_party = 'KPD';
    Q.transport_minister_party = 'KPD';

    Q.foreign_minister = 'Pieck';
    Q.interior_minister = 'Ulbricht';
    Q.justice_minister = 'Heckert';
    Q.labor_minister = 'Münzenberg';
    Q.economic_minister = 'Remmele';
    Q.finance_minister = 'Neumann';
    Q.agriculture_minister = 'Hoernle';
    Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Leber';
    Q.transport_minister = 'Hoernle';

    Q.pro_republic -= 20;
    Q.coup_progress += 5;
    Q.capital_strike_progress += 4;
    Q.reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.25;
    Q.sa_strength += 300;
    Q.sh_strength += 200;
    Q.workers_spd -= 5;
    Q.left_dissent -= 10;

} else if (Q.president === "Luther") {
    // Luther: fiscal conservative technocrat
    Q.chancellor_party = "I";
    Q.chancellor = "Luther";
    Q.presidential_cabinet = 1;
    Q.presidential_powers_active = 1;

    Q.foreign_minister_party = 'DVP';
    Q.interior_minister_party = 'Z';
    Q.justice_minister_party = 'DDP';
    Q.labor_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.economic_minister_party = 'DVP';
    Q.finance_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.agriculture_minister_party = 'CNBL';
    Q.reichswehr_minister_party = 'I';
    Q.transport_minister_party = 'I';

    Q.foreign_minister = Q.stresemann_dead ? 'Curtius' : 'Stresemann';
    Q.interior_minister = 'Wirth';
    Q.justice_minister = 'Koch-Weser';
    Q.labor_minister = 'Brauns';
    Q.economic_minister = 'Curtius';
    Q.finance_minister = 'Luther';
    Q.agriculture_minister = 'Hamkens';
    Q.reichswehr_minister = 'Groener';
    Q.transport_minister = 'von Guérard';

    Q.pro_republic -= 5;
    Q.workers_spd -= 2;
    Q.new_middle_spd += 2;

    } else if (Q.president === "Seeckt") {
    var candidates = [];

    candidates.push({name: "Seeckt",      party: "I", score: 80});
    candidates.push({name: "Schleicher",  party: "I",
        score: 65 + ((Q.schleicher_influence || 0) * 0.3)});
    candidates.push({name: "Groener",     party: "I",
        score: Q.groener_dismissed ? 20 : 55});
    candidates.push({name: "Hammerstein", party: "I",
        score: 45 + ((Q.reichswehr_loyalty || 0.5) * 20)});

    // civilian fallbacks only, no Papen
    if (Q.dvp_r >= 5) {
        candidates.push({
            name: Q.stresemann_dead ? "Curtius" : "Stresemann",
            party: "DVP", score: 30
        });
    }
    if (Q.dnvp_r >= 5 && Q.dnvp_line !== 3) {
        candidates.push({name: "Westarp", party: "DNVP", score: 25});
    }
    } else if (Q.president === "Seldte") {
    var candidates = [];

    if (Q.dnvp_r >= 5) {
        candidates.push({
            name: Q.dnvp_line === 3 ? "Hugenberg" : "Westarp",
            party: "DNVP", score: 70
        });
    }
    if (Q.nsdap_r >= 20) { // raised from 10
        candidates.push({
            name: "Hitler", party: "NSDAP",
            score: 40 + (Q.nsdap_r * 0.8)
        });
    }
    if (Q.dvp_r >= 5) {
        candidates.push({
            name: Q.stresemann_dead ? "Curtius" : "Stresemann",
            party: "DVP", score: 30
        });
    }
    // Papen as hard floor fallback — always available
    candidates.push({name: "Papen", party: "I", score: 15});

    } else if (Q.president === "Hugenberg") {
    var cam_scores = Q.camarilla_chancellor_scores || {};
    var candidates = [];

    if (Q.dnvp_r >= 5) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Hugenberg", party: "DNVP",
            score: (cam_scores["Hugenberg"] || 0) + 90
        });
    }
    if (Q.nsdap_r >= 10) {
        candidates.push({
            name: "Hitler", party: "NSDAP",
            score: (cam_scores["Hitler"] || 0) + 50 + (Q.nsdap_r * 0.5)
        });
        candidates.push({
            name: "Göring", party: "NSDAP",
            score: (cam_scores["Göring"] || 0) + 30
        });
    }
    // Hard floor — Papen as last resort compromise
    candidates.push({name: "Papen", party: "I", score: (cam_scores["Papen"] || 0) + 10});

    candidates.sort(function(a, b) {
        return (b.score * (0.85 + Math.random() * 0.3)) -
               (a.score * (0.85 + Math.random() * 0.3));
    });

    Q.chancellor       = candidates[0].name;
    Q.chancellor_party = candidates[0].party;

    // Papen appointment still triggers consequences
    if (Q.chancellor === "Papen") {
        Q.papen_cabinet     = 1;
        Q.cabinet_of_barons = 1;
        Q.coup_progress    += 2;
        Q.pro_republic     -= 8;
    }

    if (Q.chancellor === "Hitler" || Q.chancellor === "Göring") {
        Q.nazi_takeover_begins  = 1;
        Q.vice_chancellor       = "Hugenberg";
        Q.vice_chancellor_party = "DNVP";
        Q.cabinet_of_barons     = 1;
    }
    }


// Political consequences
Q.pro_republic -= 8;
Q.workers_spd -= 3;
Q.new_middle_spd -= 2;
Q.old_middle_spd -= 2;
Q.coup_progress += 1;
!}

= Presidential Crisis - Article 48 Invoked

**After [+ no_majority_elections +] consecutive failed coalition attempts, parliamentary democracy has reached an impasse.**

All major parties have repeatedly failed to build a majority government. The Reichstag has proven unable to govern.

President [+ president +] has invoked Article 48 of the Constitution to appoint a **Presidential Cabinet** - a minority government that will rule by decree rather than through parliamentary majorities.

**Appointed Chancellor:** [+ chancellor +] [? if chancellor_party != 'I' : ([+ chancellor_party +]) ?]

[? if chancellor_party = 'I' : This is a non-partisan "Presidential Cabinet" with technocratic ministers and no party affiliation. ?]

[? if president = "Hindenburg" and spd_toleration = 1 : The SPD has agreed to tolerate this government from opposition, preventing its immediate collapse through a vote of no confidence. ?]

[? if president = "Braun" : President Braun has appointed an SPD emergency government. This is an unprecedented constitutional maneuver that will be fiercely contested. ?]

[? if president = "Hitler" : President Hitler has appointed an NSDAP government. Democracy is in mortal danger. ?]

**Cabinet (Civil Service/Presidential Appointments):**
- Foreign: [+ foreign_minister +]
- Interior: [+ interior_minister +]
- Justice: [+ justice_minister +]
- Labor: [+ labor_minister +]
- Economic Affairs: [+ economic_minister +]
- Finance: [+ finance_minister +]
- Agriculture: [+ agriculture_minister +]
- Reichswehr: [+ reichswehr_minister +]

This government will rule by presidential decree rather than through normal parliamentary procedures. The Reichstag may vote no confidence at any time, but this would only trigger new elections that would likely reproduce the same deadlock.

[? if president = "Hindenburg" : Hindenburg's use of Article 48 to bypass parliamentary deadlock sets a dangerous precedent. The slow death of parliamentary democracy may have begun. ?]

[? if no_majority_elections >= 3 : After three consecutive electoral failures to produce a government, many Germans question whether parliamentary democracy can function at all. ?]

- @accept_crisis: Accept the presidential cabinet

@accept_crisis
on-arrival: coalition_dissent += 5 if spd_in_government = 0; left_dissent += 10 if spd_toleration = 1; political_crisis_level += 1

The government crisis has been resolved through authoritarian means. [? if spd_toleration = 1 : Many in our party are deeply unhappy about tolerating an undemocratic government, but it seems the only alternative to chaos or new elections that benefit extremists. ?]

[? if in_emergency_government : Our emergency government will face severe opposition. We must act quickly to stabilize the situation before our constitutional authority is challenged. ?]

Parliamentary democracy has suffered a severe blow. The road back to normal governance will be difficult.

# ============================================
# SPECIAL COALITION SCENARIOS
# ============================================

@popular_front_special
title: Attempt to form a Popular Front
subtitle: SPD + KPD + Z + [+ ddp_name +] ([+ spd_r + kpd_r + z_r + ddp_r +]%)
view-if: coalition_type = 'popular_front' and popular_front_possible = 1
on-arrival: coup_progress += 2; in_popular_front = 1; kpd_relation += 10; z_relation += 10; pro_republic += 5
achievement: volksfront

Through extraordinary negotiations, a Popular Front has been formed!

The Conciliator leadership of the KPD and the progressive leadership of Joseph Joos in the Center Party have made this historic coalition possible.

This is an unprecedented moment: Communists, Socialists, and Catholics united in defense of democracy against the Nazi threat.

However, the right-wing views this as a betrayal. Coup attempts are likely.

@left_front_special  
title: Attempt to form a Left Front
subtitle: SPD + KPD [? if sapd_formed : + SAPD ?] ([+ spd_r + kpd_r + sapd_r +]%)
view-if: coalition_type = 'left_front' and left_front_possible = 1
on-arrival: coup_progress += 3; capital_strike_progress += 2; in_left_front = 1; kpd_relation += 15; reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.1
achievement: einheitsfront

The Left Front has been formed! Workers' unity has finally been achieved.

For the first time, Social Democrats and Communists will govern together. This is either the dawn of a new socialist Germany or a disaster waiting to happen.

The bourgeois parties are horrified. Capital flight has begun. The Reichswehr is restless.

[? if sapd_formed : The SAPD's participation bridges the gap between the two larger parties. ?]

The right-wing is preparing for armed resistance.

@nazi_coalition_warning
title: The Nazis demand power
view-if: nsdap_r >= 30 and coalition_type = 'far_right'
on-arrival: coup_progress += 5; pro_republic -= 15; sa_strength += 200

**WARNING: NAZI COALITION FORMED**

[+ nsdap_leader +] has entered the government as Chancellor. The Nazis now control the apparatus of state power.

This may be the end of German democracy.

# ============================================
# KPD COALITION GOALS (if in government)
# ============================================

@kpd_coalition_demands
title: The KPD presents its coalition demands
view-if: kpd_in_government and not kpd_goals_seen
on-arrival: kpd_goals_seen = 1; kpd_coalition_dissent = 0

The Communists have agreed to join the government, but they have demands:

**KPD Coalition Goals:**

1. **Labor Ministry:** Must pursue aggressive pro-worker policies
2. **Interior Ministry:** Must crack down on fascist organizations  
3. **Economic Ministry:** Must implement socialist economic planning
4. **Finance Ministry:** Must tax the wealthy heavily

The KPD will track our progress on these goals. If we fail to meet their expectations, they may withdraw from the coalition.

[? if in_popular_front : Notably, the KPD has moderated some demands due to the Popular Front arrangement with the Center Party. ?]

[? if in_left_front : The KPD is being more aggressive in the Left Front, demanding radical changes immediately. ?]

- @accept_kpd_goals: We will work with the KPD on these goals
- @reject_kpd_goals: These demands are too extreme

@accept_kpd_goals
on-arrival: kpd_coalition_dissent -= 5; left_dissent -= 5; labor_dissent -= 5; reformist_dissent += 10; neorevisionist_dissent += 10

We have agreed to work toward the KPD's policy goals. The left wing of our party is pleased, but moderates are concerned.

@reject_kpd_goals
on-arrival: kpd_coalition_dissent += 10; kpd_relation -= 10; left_dissent += 5

We have rejected the KPD's most radical demands. They are unhappy, but remain in the coalition for now.

